    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_fusco_728958",
        "quote": "As a writer of both novels and screenplays, I can say that screenwriting is a vastly rewarding creative life - if you fight hard enough to do it on your own terms. Whether I write books or not, my screenwriting life has been creatively rewarding and remains so.",
        "author": {
            "name": "John Fusco",
            "url": "/quotes/john_fusco_728958"
        },
