    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_fusco_728951",
        "quote": "I grew up with a fascination with Marco Polo. I had this unlikely interest in the East as a young man, and you can't really read about Chinese history and philosophy without encountering him at every turn.",
        "author": {
            "name": "John Fusco",
            "url": "/quotes/john_fusco_728951"
