    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_fusco_728955",
        "quote": "In 2007, I did a horseback trip across part of central Mongolia with my 13-year-old son - we encountered Marco Polo at all these historical places where Mongolian nomads would reference his accounts and his relationship with Kublai Khan.",
        "author": {
            "name": "John Fusco",
            "url": "/quotes/john_fusco_728955"
