    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_fusco_728966",
        "quote": "I started looking into horse history books and came across the actual story of this half-breed endurance horseman and his painted mustang Hidalgo. I wasn't really sure if I was going to do the movie at that point.",
        "author": {
            "name": "John Fusco",
            "url": "/quotes/john_fusco_728966"
        },
