                "name": "Horseman",
                "url": "/topics/horseman"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_fusco_728967",
        "quote": "I grew up in the unlikely place of Connecticut. The Eastern Woodlands. It was semi-rural where I grew up. I was fascinated by the Piqua and the Mohegan Indians of that area.",
