    {
        "url": "/quotes/john_fusco_728968",
        "quote": "I wrote 'Young Guns' on spec because I really believed that the young age of these guys historically, the whole legend of Billy dying at 21, would attract a young staple of stars, and that would be the game-changer.",
        "author": {
            "name": "John Fusco",
            "url": "/quotes/john_fusco_728968"
